{"service_name": "ISO27001 and Associated Information Security Services", "service_id": "5611265904869376", "company_name": "Advent IM Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Advent IM Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     ISO27001 and Associated Information Security Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Assisting organisations with the implementation of information security management systems (ISMS) and controls aligned to industry best practice including ISO27001, ISO22301, PCI-DSS and Cyber Essentials.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Gap Analysis against systems, standards and controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk Assessment of Identified Information Assets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk Remediation Plans and Control Implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management System Development through Mentoring\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Policy Development\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Staff Awareness Training\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ongoing Internal Compliance Checking and Pre-certification Audits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Exercising and Testing of Plans\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Cardholder Data Environment Scoping\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Completion of SAQs and AoCs\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Integrated security approach security reducing duplication of effort and bureaucracy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implementing security as a business enabler rather than blocker\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Adapting methodologies to deliver agile, pragmatic and proportionate solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk is owned and managed organisation wide, not avoided\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Competitive edge when bidding for new contracts\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Mentoring approach ensures knowledge is transferred internally to client staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Tailored solutions, fit for purpose not out of a box\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent of product vendors\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Detailed knowledge of public sector organisational ways of working\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     100% track record in accreditations, certifications and approvals\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3500 to \u00a3980 per unit\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92582/5611265904869376-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92582/5611265904869376-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92582/5611265904869376-service-definit